</node>
<node id="GVG副本">
  <data key="d0">GVG副本</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">GVG副本是一个游戏内活动，具有开启和关闭的有效时间，玩家在副本内进行战斗，结束时根据积分结算奖励。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="副本积分">
  <data key="d0">副本积分</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">副本积分是GVG副本中用于记录对战双方联盟当前得分的数据，通过蓝、红颜色文本框在UI界面上区分显示。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="副本有效时间">
  <data key="d0">副本有效时间</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">副本有效时间是GVG副本从开启到关闭的预设时长，在副本中以倒计时方式显示，归零时所有玩家被移出副本。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="副本战报">
  <data key="d0">副本战报</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">副本战报是GVG副本中争夺建筑战斗的记录，会发送给相关玩家并缓存在建筑中供双方查看，格式与沙盘战报相同。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="GVG副本UI界面">
  <data key="d0">GVG副本UI界面</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">GVG副本UI界面是在玩家主界面顶部中央增加的显示组件，用于展示副本积分和有效时间倒计时。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="GVG活动界面">
  <data key="d0">GVG活动界面</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">GVG活动界面是玩家进入或查看GVG副本状态的交互界面，在副本结束后显示活动结束状态。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="GVG副本奖励">
  <data key="d0">GVG副本奖励</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">GVG副本奖励是副本活动结束后系统发放给参赛联盟成员的奖励，分为获胜方和战败方两大类，每类包含参战与未参战成员奖励。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="系统邮件">
  <data key="d0">系统邮件</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">系统邮件是GVG副本奖励的发放方式，所有类型的奖励都通过此途径发送给玩家。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="GVG观战功能">
  <data key="d0">GVG观战功能</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">GVG观战功能允许未报名的玩家在副本开启后进入战场观看战斗，可以拖动和缩放场景，但不支持查看战报详情。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="关卡编辑器">
  <data key="d0">关卡编辑器</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">关卡编辑器是用于设计游戏关卡的工具，包含黑板功能，可以加载外部配置表数据供触发器和条件使用。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="黑板功能">
  <data key="d0">黑板功能</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">黑板功能是关卡编辑器的一部分，用于加载指定的玩法配置表，管理多个触发器之间的数据，其数据在编辑器界面中可见并可选择。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="编辑器配置文件">
  <data key="d0">编辑器配置文件</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">编辑器配置文件是关卡编辑器的设置文件，用于定义编辑器各功能加载的表格和工具自身参数。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="玩法配置表">
  <data key="d0">玩法配置表</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">玩法配置表是存储游戏玩法规则和参数的数据表格，可以被关卡编辑器的黑板功能加载和使用。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="部队训练">
  <data key="d0">部队训练</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">部队训练是一种游戏内活动，用于提升部队能力，但不会对副本内的状态产生实时影响。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="科技研究">
  <data key="d0">科技研究</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">科技研究是一种游戏内活动，用于解锁或升级科技，但不会对副本内的状态产生实时影响。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="英雄升级">
  <data key="d0">英雄升级</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">英雄升级是一种游戏内活动，用于提升英雄属性或能力，但不会对副本内的状态产生实时影响。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="技能升级">
  <data key="d0">技能升级</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">技能升级是一种游戏内活动，用于提升技能效果，但不会对副本内的状态产生实时影响。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="玩家个人数据">
  <data key="d0">玩家个人数据</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">玩家个人数据是记录玩家状态和进度的信息，在副本内通常不实时更新，需要额外开发沟通才能实现。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="GVG玩法配置表">
  <data key="d0">GVG玩法配置表</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">GVG玩法配置表是存储GVG副本相关设置(如有效时间)的数据表格，用于游戏系统的配置。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="建筑">
  <data key="d0">建筑</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">建筑是GVG副本中可以被争夺的目标，其战报会被缓存，供对战双方玩家查看。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="沙盘战报">
  <data key="d0">沙盘战报</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">沙盘战报是一种战报格式，GVG副本内战报的格式与此相同。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="我方联盟">
  <data key="d0">我方联盟</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">我方联盟是GVG副本中对战的一方，在UI界面上其积分用蓝色文本框表示。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="对方联盟">
  <data key="d0">对方联盟</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">对方联盟是GVG副本中对战的另一方，在UI界面上其积分用红色文本框表示。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="获胜联盟">
  <data key="d0">获胜联盟</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">获胜联盟是在GVG副本结束时积分更高的一方，在活动结束界面上其信息区域会显示“胜利”文本。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="参战成员">
  <data key="d0">参战成员</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">参战成员是GVG副本中实际参与了战斗的联盟玩家，有资格获得特定的参战成员奖励。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="未参战成员">
  <data key="d0">未参战成员</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">未参战成员是GVG副本中属于参赛联盟但未实际参与战斗的玩家，有资格获得特定的未参战成员奖励。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="触发器">
  <data key="d0">触发器</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">触发器是关卡编辑器中的功能组件，可以使用黑板加载的配置表数据作为其参数。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="条件">
  <data key="d0">条件</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">条件是关卡编辑器中的功能组件，可以使用黑板加载的配置表数据作为其参数。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8dd9515066c411f750e7a718d62badfd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="GVG">
  <data key="d0">GVG</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">GVG is a competitive event involving alliances, featuring stages like registration, matching, and a battle instance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Matching Phase">
  <data key="d0">Matching Phase</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The stage following registration where the system pairs alliances against each other as opponents.&lt;SEP&gt;The Matching Phase is a stage in the GVG event where the system pairs alliances against each other and sends notifications to players.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29eecccea7490051a78857d0a2121a87</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Notification Email">
  <data key="d0">Notification Email</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">An email sent to players to inform them about the status of the GVG activity, such as the start or end of the matching phase.&lt;SEP&gt;A Notification Email is sent to all alliance members each time a GVG registration or registration update is successfully completed, containing the selected session times and participant list.&lt;SEP&gt;Notification Emails are sent to players at the start and end of the Matching Phase to inform them about the status of opponent matching.&lt;SEP&gt;Messages sent to all players of both alliances to inform them of the GvG instance's opening and closing.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29eecccea7490051a78857d0a2121a87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-978055161286ec0d66cfcb71c8e04785</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="UI Interface">
  <data key="d0">UI Interface</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The UI Interface is the player-facing screen that displays information such as countdown timers, alliance details, and opponent information during the GVG event.&lt;SEP&gt;The user interface for the GvG instance activity, displaying opponent information and providing 'Enter' or 'Spectate' buttons based on the player's status.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-978055161286ec0d66cfcb71c8e04785</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Alliance">
  <data key="d0">Alliance</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">A group of players that can register for the GVG activity, subject to conditions like server ranking or member count.&lt;SEP&gt;A group of players that can register and participate in the GVG activity.&lt;SEP&gt;An Alliance is a player organization that must meet specific conditions to be eligible to register for the GVG activity.&lt;SEP&gt;A social guild or group whose members can sign up for GVG activities and are organized into teams.&lt;SEP&gt;An Alliance is a player group that participates in GVG, with attributes like name, power, participant count, and server ID.&lt;SEP&gt;An Alliance is a player group that participates in the GVG instance, competing for control of buildings and accumulating points.&lt;SEP&gt;A group of players that participates in the GvG instance, with members either fighting or spectating based on the participation list.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29eecccea7490051a78857d0a2121a87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a512646597d2b7b2699f5e2e5c8f4a4e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-978055161286ec0d66cfcb71c8e04785&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-87d8ac677645393e5a5073d98d4850f1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe1fd6e30ee3ce0c5ba91f5585fb3840</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Opponent Alliance">
  <data key="d0">Opponent Alliance</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Opponent Alliance is the matched rival in GVG, whose details are initially hidden and later revealed.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Battle Instance">
  <data key="d0">Battle Instance</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The Battle Instance is the GVG combat stage that opens at a scheduled time, allowing players to enter and engage in battle.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Player">
  <data key="d0">Player</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">An individual user who is a member of an alliance and can be selected for GVG activity participation.&lt;SEP&gt;An individual user who interacts with the GVG activity system, specifically the one who clicks the registration button and whose alliance and rank are checked for eligibility.&lt;SEP&gt;An individual participant who can be a member of an alliance and may enter the GVG instance.&lt;SEP&gt;A Player is a user who participates in the game, can be a member of an Alliance, and may be selected for the GVG activity registration list.&lt;SEP&gt;A Player is an individual participant who can be selected for GVG, must meet entry conditions, and can enter the battle instance.&lt;SEP&gt;A Player is an individual participant in the GVG instance who can attack buildings with personal or rallied troops.&lt;SEP&gt;A participant in the game who must meet specific conditions to enter the GvG instance and whose actions are restricted in the original server during the instance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29eecccea7490051a78857d0a2121a87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a512646597d2b7b2699f5e2e5c8f4a4e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-978055161286ec0d66cfcb71c8e04785&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-87d8ac677645393e5a5073d98d4850f1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe1fd6e30ee3ce0c5ba91f5585fb3840</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Entry Conditions">
  <data key="d0">Entry Conditions</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Entry Conditions are requirements a player must meet to enter the GVG battle instance, such as being selected and having no active troops.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Shield Effect">
  <data key="d0">Shield Effect</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Shield Effect is a protective status automatically applied to a player's main city in their home server upon first entering the GVG instance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Odd Alliance">
  <data key="d0">Odd Alliance</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">An Odd Alliance is an alliance that remains unpaired after the matching process and is automatically marked as winning by default in the next stage.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bye Win">
  <data key="d0">Bye Win</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A rule where an alliance with no opponent after matching is automatically marked as the winner for that stage.&lt;SEP&gt;A Bye Win is the automatic victory granted to an Odd Alliance when it cannot be matched with an opponent.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29eecccea7490051a78857d0a2121a87</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Home Server">
  <data key="d0">Home Server</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The Home Server is the player's original game server where their main city is located and where certain restrictions apply during GVG.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Main City">
  <data key="d0">Main City</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The Main City is the player's primary settlement in their Home Server, which receives a Shield Effect during GVG and cannot be in combat for the player to enter the instance.&lt;SEP&gt;The player's primary settlement in the original server, which must not be in combat status and receives a shield when the player enters a GvG instance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-978055161286ec0d66cfcb71c8e04785</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Countdown Timer">
  <data key="d0">Countdown Timer</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Countdown Timer is a UI element displayed centrally that shows the remaining time until matching completes or the battle instance opens.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Help Text">
  <data key="d0">Help Text</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Help Text is informational content displayed at the bottom center of the UI interface to guide players.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Enter Button">
  <data key="d0">Enter Button</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Enter Button is an interactive UI element that players manually click to enter the GVG battle instance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Exit Button">
  <data key="d0">Exit Button</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Exit Button allows a player to leave the GVG battle instance and return to their Home Server.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Player City">
  <data key="d0">Player City</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">A Player City is a player's settlement within the GVG battle instance, which remains attackable even if the player leaves and re-enters.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Troops">
  <data key="d0">Troops</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Troops are military units created by a player; having any troops prevents the player from entering the GVG battle instance.&lt;SEP&gt;Military units created by a player. A player cannot have any troops created to meet the entry condition for the GvG instance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-978055161286ec0d66cfcb71c8e04785</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Inner City Hospital">
  <data key="d0">Inner City Hospital</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Inner City Hospital is a building where wounded soldiers are treated; it must contain no wounded soldiers for the player to enter GVG.&lt;SEP&gt;A building within the player's city that must not contain any wounded soldiers (either being treated or treatment completed) for the player to enter the GvG instance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-978055161286ec0d66cfcb71c8e04785</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Wounded Soldiers">
  <data key="d0">Wounded Soldiers</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Wounded Soldiers are military units undergoing or finished with treatment in the Inner City Hospital; their presence blocks GVG entry.&lt;SEP&gt;Injured units within the Inner City Hospital. Their absence is a prerequisite for a player to enter the GvG instance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fb8c70f0427ab727390ab4ab71583f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-978055161286ec0d66cfcb71c8e04785</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Game Main Interface">
  <data key="d0">Game Main Interface</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Game Main Interface is the primary screen from which the GVG activity interface is accessed.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="GVG Activity Interface">
  <data key="d0">GVG Activity Interface</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The GVG Activity Interface displays the current activity stage name, the GVG activity instance's opening and closing times, and the time remaining until the next stage begins.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Preview Stage">
  <data key="d0">Preview Stage</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The Preview Stage is the initial phase of the GVG activity where the registration stage is not yet open, and the UI only shows the activity name and the time remaining until registration opens.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Registration Stage">
  <data key="d0">Registration Stage</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The Registration Stage is a designated period during the GVG activity where eligible alliances can register themselves and selected members into the instance server matching queue for the next stage.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Registration Button">
  <data key="d0">Registration Button</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Registration Button is a UI element within the activity interface that players click to initiate the registration process during the GVG Registration Stage.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Registration Details Interface">
  <data key="d0">Registration Details Interface</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Registration Details Interface is opened by clicking the registration button and allows players to select battle sessions and participating alliance members.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Battle Session">
  <data key="d0">Battle Session</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">A Battle Session is a scheduled time slot for GVG instance battles, configured to accommodate global players across different UTC time zones.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Matching System">
  <data key="d0">Matching System</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">The Matching System adjusts the final battle session time for an alliance based on the time slots and quantity selected during registration, according to predefined rules.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Registration List">
  <data key="d0">Registration List</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The Registration List is the roster of all alliance members at the moment the alliance first submits its registration for the GVG activity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Submit Registration Button">
  <data key="d0">Submit Registration Button</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Submit Registration Button is clicked by players to finalize and submit their GVG activity registration after selecting battle sessions and members.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="GVG Configuration Table">
  <data key="d0">GVG Configuration Table</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The GVG Configuration Table is a data file where project teams configure settings such as eligibility conditions, required alliance ranks, the number of battle sessions (M), and the maximum selectable sessions (N).</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Alliance Permission Table">
  <data key="d0">Alliance Permission Table</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Alliance Permission Table configures which alliance ranks are granted the authority to perform GVG registration.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="GVG Gameplay Rules Table">
  <data key="d0">GVG Gameplay Rules Table</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The GVG Gameplay Rules Table is a newly created configuration file that specifies the alliance ranks required for GVG registration.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Level Editor File">
  <data key="d0">Level Editor File</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">A file that needs to be modified alongside the configuration table to change the maximum number of participants.&lt;SEP&gt;The Level Editor File is a configuration document that must be modified alongside the configuration table to increase the maximum number of registrants for the GVG activity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-87d8ac677645393e5a5073d98d4850f1</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="GVG Activity">
  <data key="d0">GVG Activity</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">A competitive event for alliances that requires registration, has specific participation conditions, and involves multiple sessions.&lt;SEP&gt;A competitive event where alliances can sign up and participate, involving stages like registration and matching.&lt;SEP&gt;A series of structured events including announcement, sign-up, matching, instance opening, and results display for guild competition.&lt;SEP&gt;The GVG Activity is a recurring competitive event in the game involving alliances, with stages including Preview and Registration, leading to instance battles.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29eecccea7490051a78857d0a2121a87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-87d8ac677645393e5a5073d98d4850f1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe1fd6e30ee3ce0c5ba91f5585fb3840</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d5">1772784706</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="UTC Time">
  <data key="d0">UTC Time</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">UTC Time is the standard time reference used to schedule multiple Battle Sessions for the GVG activity to accommodate a global player base.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b</data>
