  <data key="d2">Instance Points are the sole criterion for determining the winning alliance in a GVG instance, accumulated through various actions.&lt;SEP&gt;Points earned by an alliance in the GvG instance through actions like capturing buildings or defeating enemy player troops, contributing to the total score.</data>
