</edge>
<edge source="Alliance" target="Alliance Permission Table">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Alliance Permission Table configures which ranks within an Alliance have the authority to perform GVG registration.</data>
  <data key="d9">authority delegation,rank management</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b</data>
  <data key="d11">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d12">1772784707</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Alliance" target="GVG Gameplay Rules Table">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The GVG Gameplay Rules Table specifies the alliance ranks required for a player to have GVG registration permissions.</data>
  <data key="d9">requirement specification,rule enforcement</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b</data>
  <data key="d11">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d12">1772784707</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Alliance" target="Player">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Players are members of an alliance and can be selected or deselected for the GVG activity sign-up list.&lt;SEP&gt;Players are members of an Alliance, and the Alliance organizes them into teams for GVG participation.&lt;SEP&gt;Players are members of an Alliance, and the Alliance's member list is used to create the GVG Registration List.&lt;SEP&gt;A Player belongs to an Alliance. All players in both Alliances receive Notification Emails about the GvG Instance's status.</data>
  <data key="d9">membership,notification,organization,selection,team formation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-74f71c3c343b0c80da741521a4a6e19b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29eecccea7490051a78857d0a2121a87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-978055161286ec0d66cfcb71c8e04785&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe1fd6e30ee3ce0c5ba91f5585fb3840</data>
  <data key="d11">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d12">1772784707</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Alliance" target="Registration Phase">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Alliances participate in the GVG activity by submitting their sign-up lists during the Registration Phase.</data>
  <data key="d9">participation,submission</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-29eecccea7490051a78857d0a2121a87</data>
  <data key="d11">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d12">1772784707</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Alliance" target="Sign-Up List">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">An alliance manages and submits its Sign-Up List containing selected players for the GVG activity.</data>
  <data key="d9">management,submission</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-29eecccea7490051a78857d0a2121a87</data>
  <data key="d11">D:\work\A_elex\策划表\doctment\processed\20260306_150640\GVG功能制作文档</data>
  <data key="d12">1772784707</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Alliance" target="Neutral Buildings">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Alliances compete to occupy Neutral Buildings, which then periodically generate points for the occupying alliance.</data>
  <data key="d9">point generation,territorial control</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-a512646597d2b7b2699f5e2e5c8f4a4e</data>
