</edge>
<edge source="Player" target="Main City">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">A Player owns and operates a Main City in their Home Server.&lt;SEP&gt;A Player owns a Main City, which must not be in a combat state as a prerequisite for entering the GvG Instance.</data>
  <data key="d9">ownership,primary settlement,status check</data>
