  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Main City" target="Protective Shield">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">A Player's Main City automatically gains a Protective Shield when the player first enters a GvG Instance, lasting until the instance ends.</data>
